         xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
         xmlns:ns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
  <title>LAMMPS data files</title>

  <para>OVITO can import data files written by the <link
  xlink:href="http://lammps.sandia.gov">LAMMPS molecular dynamics
  package</link>.</para>

  <para>Only data files in the <literal>atomic</literal> format of LAMMPS are
  supported.</para>

  <para>Compressed files (having a <filename>.gz</filename> suffix) are
  automatically decompressed on the fly.</para>
</section>
